>White, Ancient Letters (1986), 93.</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="fr" default="NO"><head lang="de">Französisch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Burnet, L'Égypte ancienne (2003), Nr. 143</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.21292" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="low" full="yes">Oxyrhynchos oder Hermopolis</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>